<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>360° — أدوات الزوايا السعرية الزمنية</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@300;400;600;700;900&family=Noto+Kufi+Arabic:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://telegram.org/js/telegram-web-app.js"></script>
<script src="calculations.js" defer></script>
<script src="macro-risk.js" defer></script>
<script src="quant-scanners.js" defer></script>
<script src="time-frameworks.js" defer></script>
<script src="astro-lenses.js" defer></script>
<script src="geom-smc-patch.js" defer></script>
<style>
/* اعتماد الألوان الصارمة: أسود، أبيض، وبرتقالي فقط وتدرجات الرمادي المحايد */
:root {
  --bg: #000000;
  --s: #0d0d0d;
  --s2: #141414;
  --b: #2a2a2a;
  --t: #ffffff;
  --t2: #cccccc;
  --t3: #888888;
  --o: #ff6a00;
  --o2: #ff8c33;
  --od: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.15);
  --rd: 14px;
}
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; overscroll-behavior-y: none; }
body { font-family: 'Noto Kufi Arabic', 'Cairo', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--t); line-height: 1.7; overflow-x: hidden; overscroll-behavior-y: none; }


::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 5px; }
::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--bg); }
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--b); border-radius: 9px; }
a { color: var(--o); text-decoration: none; }

/* Header & Navigation */
.top { position: fixed; top: 0; right: 0; left: 0; z-index: 999; height: 52px; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b); display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 1rem; gap: 0.6rem; }
.top-logo { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--o); cursor: pointer; }
.top-nav { display: flex; gap: 0.15rem; margin: 0 auto; }
.top-nav a { padding: 0.35rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 7px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--t2); transition: all 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; cursor: pointer; }
.top-nav a:hover { color: var(--t); background: var(--s2); }
.top-nav a.active { color: var(--o); background: var(--od); }

/* User Menu */
.top-user { position: relative; cursor: pointer; }
.top-a { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--o); padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem 0.2rem 0.2rem; border: 1.5px solid var(--o); border-radius: 20px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.top-a:hover { background: var(--o); color: var(--bg); }
.top-a img { width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 1px solid var(--o); background: var(--bg); }
.user-menu { display: none; position: absolute; top: calc(100% + 5px); left: 0; background: var(--s); border: 1px solid var(--b); border-radius: 9px; padding: 0.5rem; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; min-width: 130px; z-index: 1000; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
.user-menu.open { display: flex; }
.user-menu a { color: var(--t); font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none; text-align: center; border: 1px solid var(--b); transition: 0.2s; font-weight: 600; }
.user-menu a:hover { background: var(--od); color: var(--o); border-color: var(--o); }

.mbtn { display: none; background: none; border: none; color: var(--t); font-size: 1.3rem; cursor: pointer; }
.mnav { display: none; position: fixed; top: 52px; right: 0; left: 0; background: var(--s); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b); z-index: 998; padding: 0.6rem; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.15rem; }
.mnav.open { display: flex; }
.mnav a { padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 7px; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--t2); cursor: pointer; }
.mnav a.active { color: var(--o); background: var(--od); }
.pg { display: none; padding-top: 52px; min-height: 100vh; animation: fi 0.3s ease; }
.pg.active { display: block; }
@keyframes fi { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

/* Hero Section */
.hero { min-height: calc(100vh - 52px); display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; padding: 1.5rem 1rem; }
.hero-grid { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: linear-gradient(var(--b) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, var(--b) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 60px 60px; opacity: 0.2; }
.hero-glow { position: absolute; width: 400px; height: 400px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,106,0,0.15), transparent 70%); top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
.hero-top { position: relative; z-index: 2; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.hero-big { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 900; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5.5rem); color: var(--o); line-height: 1; }
.hero-tt { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.3rem); margin-top: 0.2rem; color: var(--t); }
.hero-sub { color: var(--t2); font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 0.3rem; }

/* Halving & Widgets */
.halving { position: relative; z-index: 2; background: var(--s); border: 1px solid var(--b); border-radius: var(--rd); padding: 1rem 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; max-width: 600px; width: 100%; }
.halving-title { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 600; }
.halving-nums { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.halving-box { text-align: center; }
.halving-box .n { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--o); line-height: 1; }
.halving-box .l { font-size: 0.6rem; color: #ffffff; }
.halving-bar { width: 100%; height: 6px; background: var(--s2); border-radius: 3px; margin-top: 0.6rem; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--b); }
.halving-bar-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--o); border-radius: 3px; transition: width 1s; }
/* شبكة الأدوات المصغرة (مؤشر الخوف + الإغلاق) */
.hero-widgets {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
  gap: 0.6rem;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  z-index: 2;
}
.widget-box {
  background: var(--s);
  border: 1px solid var(--b);
  border-radius: var(--rd);
  padding: 1rem 0.5rem;
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
  height: 100%;
}
.widget-box:hover {
  border-color: var(--o);
}
.digital-clock {
  font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  color: var(--o);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.4);
  line-height: 1;
  margin: 10px 0;
}
/* تصغير مقاس مؤشر الخوف ليناسب النصف */
.gauge-wrap-mini { transform: scale(0.7); margin: -15px 0; }

/* Fear Gauge */
.gauge-wrap { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin: 0.5rem 0; }
.gauge { position: relative; width: 200px; height: 110px; overflow: hidden; }
.gauge-bg { width: 200px; height: 100px; border-radius: 100px 100px 0 0; background: conic-gradient(from 180deg at 50% 100%, var(--b) 0deg, var(--t2) 90deg, var(--o) 180deg); position: relative; }
.gauge-mask { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 15px; right: 15px; height: 70px; border-radius: 70px 70px 0 0; background: var(--s); }
.gauge-needle { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 50%; width: 3px; height: 80px; background: var(--t); border-radius: 2px; transform-origin: bottom center; transform: rotate(0deg); transition: transform 1s ease; }
.gauge-val { position: absolute; bottom: 5px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--o); }
.gauge-label { text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--t); margin-top: 0.2rem; font-weight: 700; }

/* Tool strip */
.hstrip { position: relative; z-index: 2; width: 100%; max-width: 900px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 0.6rem; }
.tc { background: var(--s); border: 1px solid var(--b); border-radius: var(--rd); padding: 1rem 0.8rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; text-align: center; }
.tc:hover { border-color: var(--o); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); }
.tc-i { width: 46px; height: 46px; margin: 0 auto 12px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--od); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.3s; }
.tc-i svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; stroke: var(--o); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5px; stroke-linecap: round; stroke-linejoin: round; }
.tc-n { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.78rem; margin-bottom: 0.15rem; color: var(--t); }
.tc-d { font-size: 0.62rem; color: var(--t2); line-height: 1.4; }

/* General Pages */
.tp { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.5rem 1rem 3rem; }
.th { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-top: 1rem; }
.th h1 { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--o); }
.th p { color: var(--t2); font-size: 0.82rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; }
.ig { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.ig label { display: block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--t2); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
.ir { display: flex; gap: 0.6rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.ir .ig { flex: 1; min-width: 160px; }
input[type="number"], input[type="text"], input[type="date"], select { width: 100%; padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem; background: var(--bg); border: 1.5px solid var(--b); border-radius: 9px; color: var(--t); font-family: inherit; font-size: 0.88rem; outline: none; -moz-appearance: textfield; transition: border-color 0.2s; color-scheme: dark; }
input::-webkit-outer-spin-button, input::-webkit-inner-spin-button { -webkit-appearance: none; }
input:focus, select:focus { border-color: var(--o); }
select { cursor: pointer; } 
select option { background: var(--s); color: var(--t); }
input[type="date"] {
  direction: ltr;
  text-align: right;
  max-width: 100%;
}
.btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.3rem; padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem; background: var(--o); color: #000; font-family: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; border: none; border-radius: 9px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; }
.btn:hover { background: var(--o2); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(255,106,0,0.3); }
.btn2 { background: var(--s); color: var(--o); border: 1.5px solid var(--b); }
.btn2:hover { border-color: var(--o); background: var(--od); color: var(--t); }
.br { display: flex; gap: 0.6rem; margin-top: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

.rc { background: var(--s); border: 1px solid var(--b); border-radius: var(--rd); padding: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; animation: fi 0.3s ease; }
.rc h3 { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 700; color: var(--o); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
.rc h3::before { content: ''; width: 5px; height: 5px; background: var(--o); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
.rt { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
.rt th { text-align: center; padding: 0.45rem 0.5rem; background: var(--s2); color: var(--t); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b); }
.rt td { text-align: center; padding: 0.5rem 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--b); font-size: 0.82rem; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; color: var(--t); }
.rt tr:hover td { background: var(--s2); }

/* Shapes */
.shape-result { text-align: center; padding: 1.2rem; }
.shape-visual { width: 80px; height: 80px; border: 3px solid var(--o); margin: 0 auto 0.8rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--o); }
.shape-visual.v-circle { border-radius: 50%; } .shape-visual.v-square { border-radius: 6px; } .shape-visual.v-pentagon { border-radius: 35%; } .shape-visual.v-hexagon { border-radius: 25%; transform: rotate(30deg); } .shape-visual.v-other { border-radius: 15%; }
.shape-visual.v-line { width: 100px; height: 5px; background: var(--o); border: none; }
.shape-visual.v-triangle { border: none; width: 0; height: 0; border-left: 40px solid transparent; border-right: 40px solid transparent; border-bottom: 70px solid var(--o); }
.shape-big { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--t); }
.shape-en { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--t3); }
.sprops { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px, 1fr)); gap: 0.6rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
.sp { background: var(--s2); border-radius: 9px; padding: 0.7rem; text-align: center; border: 1px solid var(--b); }
.sp-l { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--t3); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
.sp-v { font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--o); }

.cyc-vis { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.25rem; margin: 1rem 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.cyc-d { width: 40px; height: 40px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--b); border-radius: 8px; font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--t); }
.cyc-d.active { border-color: var(--o); color: var(--o); background: var(--od); }
.cyc-arr { color: var(--t3); font-size: 0.9rem; }

/* Moon Calendar Modal */
.moon-modal { display: none; position: fixed; inset: 0; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); z-index: 10000; justify-content: center; align-items: center; padding: 1rem; backdrop-filter: blur(5px); }
.moon-modal.open { display: flex; }
.moon-wrap { background: var(--s); border: 1px solid var(--o); border-radius: var(--rd); width: 100%; max-width: 450px; padding: 1.2rem; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); }
.moon-close { position: absolute; top: 12px; right: 15px; color: var(--o); font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1; }
.moon-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--t); font-family: 'Cairo'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; direction: ltr; }
.moon-nav-btn { background: var(--s2); border: 1px solid var(--b); color: var(--o); width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: 0.2s; padding: 0; }
.moon-nav-btn:hover { background: var(--od); border-color: var(--o); }
.moon-week { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 4px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--t2); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 5px; direction: ltr; }
.moon-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr); gap: 4px; direction: ltr; }
.moon-cell { background: var(--s2); border: 1px solid var(--b); border-radius: 5px; padding: 4px 2px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; min-height: 75px; justify-content: space-between; }
.moon-cell.empty { background: transparent; border-color: transparent; }
.moon-date { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--t); font-weight: bold; align-self: flex-start; padding-left: 4px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.moon-phase-name { font-size: 0.55rem; color: var(--t); margin-top: 4px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.1; font-weight: 600; }

@media(max-width: 768px) { .top-nav { display: none; } .mbtn { display: block; } .hstrip { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } .ir { flex-direction: column; } .ir .ig { min-width: 100%; } }
/* هندسة واجهة GARCH */
.garch-bounds-panel {
    background-color: #121212;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}
.bound-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 15px;
}
.bound-row.upper-bound {
    border-right: 4px solid #ff9800;
    color: #e0e0e0;
}
.bound-row.current-price {
    background-color: #1e1e1e;
    border-right: 4px solid #ffffff;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: bold;
}
.bound-row.lower-bound {
    border-right: 4px solid #ff9800;
    color: #e0e0e0;
}

.bound-value {
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}
.garch-conclusion-box {
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    padding: 16px;
    border-right: 3px solid #ff9800; 
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #cccccc;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: right;
}
.garch-highlight {
    color: #ff9800;
    font-weight: bold;
}

@media(max-width: 480px) { .hstrip { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
.live-dot {
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  position: relative;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}
.live-dot::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: -1px; left: -1px; right: -1px; bottom: -1px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: conic-gradient(transparent 250deg, var(--o) 360deg);
  animation: radarSweep 1.5s linear infinite;
}
@keyframes radarSweep {
  0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
  100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

/* 🔸 هندسة الشاشة المركزية للبيتكوين 🔸 */
.hero-btc-card {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #111111 0%, #020202 100%);
  border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
  border-bottom: none; /* إزالة الحد السفلي ليلتصق بالشريط مباشرة */
  border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
  padding: 20px 20px 0 20px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  overflow: hidden;
  touch-action: pan-y;
}

.hero-btc-card::before {
  content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 30px 30px; background-position: center bottom;
  transform: perspective(500px) rotateX(40deg) scale(1.2); transform-origin: bottom; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
}
.hero-btc-card::after {
  content: ''; position: absolute; top: -50px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 80%; height: 100px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(255,106,0,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
}

.hbc-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; position: relative; z-index: 2; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-bottom: 15px; }
.hbc-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
.hbc-title-wrap { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.hbc-live-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--o); border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--o); animation: pulseDot 1.5s infinite alternate; }
.hbc-title { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; letter-spacing: 1px; }
.hbc-title span { color: var(--o); }
.hbc-subtitle { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; color: #666; letter-spacing: 1px; }

.hbc-price-wrap { text-align: right; direction: ltr; } 
.hbc-price { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.6rem); font-weight: 900; color: #fff; line-height: 1; text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,255,255,0.1); letter-spacing: -1px; transition: color 0.3s ease; }
.hbc-change { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 6px; display: inline-block; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 6px; transition: all 0.3s ease; }

.hbc-stat-lbl { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.55rem; color: #666; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
.hbc-stat-val { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: bold; color: #ccc; }

.hbc-chart-wrap { width: calc(100% + 40px); margin-left: -20px; height: 140px; position: relative; z-index: 10; cursor: crosshair; }
#hbc-line { transition: d 0.1s linear; }
#hbc-area { transition: points 0.1s linear; }
#hbc-pulse { animation: radarPing 2s infinite cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1); transform-origin: center; }

.hbc-tooltip { position: absolute; top: -10px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); border: 1px solid var(--o); color: #fff; font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: bold; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; pointer-events: none; display: none; z-index: 10; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); white-space: nowrap; direction: ltr; }

@keyframes pulseDot { 0% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.8); } 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.2); } }
@keyframes radarPing { 0% { r: 4.5; opacity: 0.8; stroke-width: 2; } 100% { r: 35; opacity: 0; stroke-width: 0; } }

/* شريط الاستحواذ (تم تفعيل ظهوره بشكل حاسم) */
.ticker-wrap-2 {
    width: 100%; max-width: 600px; height: 35px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto !important;
    background-color: #030303; border: 1px solid #1a1a1a; border-top: 1px solid #222;
    border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap;
    position: relative; direction: ltr; box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index: 2;
    display: block !important;
}
.ticker-track-2 { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; height: 100%; animation: ticker-move-reverse 20s linear infinite; }
.ticker-track-2:hover { animation-play-state: paused; }
.ticker-item-2 { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 15px; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; }
.t-lbl { color: #ff9800; padding-right: 4px; }
.t-val { color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; }
.t-pos { color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; }
.t-neg { color: #ff6a00; font-weight: bold; }
.t-sep { color: #444444; margin: 0 12px; font-weight: bold; }
@keyframes ticker-move-reverse { 0% { transform: translateX(-50%); } 100% { transform: translateX(0); } }


/* هندسة الشريط المعاكس */
.ticker-wrap-2 {
    width: 100%;
    height: 35px; /* ارتفاع أقل قليلاً لمنح الواجهة تبايناً هرمياً */
    background-color: #030303; /* لون أغمق بدرجة واحدة لفصل البيانات */
    border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
    border-top: none; /* دمج هندسي مع الشريط العلوي */
    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; /* تدوير الزوايا السفلية فقط */
    overflow: hidden;
    white-space: nowrap;
    position: relative;
    direction: ltr;
}

.ticker-track-2 {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100%;
    /* الحركة العكسية */
    animation: ticker-move-reverse 20s linear infinite; 
}

.ticker-track-2:hover {
    animation-play-state: paused;
}

.ticker-item-2 {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 15px;
    font-family: sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px; /* خط أصغر قليلاً للبيانات الثانوية */
}

/* القاموس اللوني للبيانات */
.t-lbl { color: #ff9800; padding-right: 4px; } /* المسميات بالبرتقالي */
.t-val { color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; } /* القيم الرقمية بالأبيض */
.t-pos { color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; } /* الارتفاع بالأبيض مع السهم */
.t-neg { color: #ff6a00; font-weight: bold; } /* الانخفاض بالبرتقالي مع السهم */
.t-sep { color: #444444; margin: 0 12px; font-weight: bold; } /* النقطة الفاصلة */

/* المحرك الفيزيائي للحركة العكسية (من اليسار لليمين) */
@keyframes ticker-move-reverse {
    0% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    100% { transform: translateX(0); }
}


/* --- تنسيقات وحدة إدارة المخاطر --- */
.risk-tabs { display: flex; gap: 8px; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 15px; padding-bottom: 5px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--t3); scrollbar-width: none; }
.risk-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
.risk-tab { background: transparent; border: 1px solid transparent; color: var(--t2); padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 0.8rem; transition: 0.3s; }
.risk-tab.active { border: 1px solid var(--o); color: #fff; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 2px rgba(255, 153, 0, 0.3)); }
.risk-panel { display: none; animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease; }
.risk-panel.active { display: block; }
.risk-btn-group { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 5px; }
.risk-btn { background: transparent; border: 1px solid var(--t3); color: var(--t2); padding: 6px 0; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.8rem; flex: 1; transition: 0.2s; }
.risk-btn.active { border-color: var(--o); color: var(--o); }
.res-box { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid var(--t3); padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 15px; border-right: 3px solid var(--o); }
.res-lbl { color: var(--t2); font-size: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 3px; }
.res-val { color: var(--o); font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.res-sub { color: #fff; font-size: 0.8rem; }
.err-msg { color: #ff4444; font-size: 0.75rem; display: none; margin-top: 5px; }
/* هندسة زر جلسات السوق والنافذة المنبثقة */
.session-btn {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1px solid var(--o);
  color: #ffffff;
  padding: 4px 14px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-family: sans-serif;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-weight: bold;
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  min-width: 80px;
}
.session-btn:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.1);
}
/* إعادة هندسة زر القائمة لمعالجة الشذوذ البصري */
.mbtn {
  display: flex !important;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 0 !important;
  margin-left: -8px !important; /* سحب العنصر لليسار لمعادلة الحافة */
  font-size: 28px !important;
  line-height: 1 !important;
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  background: transparent !important;
  border: none !important;
  color: #ffffff !important;
}

/* تنسيقات المربعات الجديدة بجوار الشعار */
.h-new-box {
  width: 38px; height: 38px;
  background: #0d0d0d;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}
.h-new-box:hover {
  background: #141414;
  border-color: var(--o);
}
.h-new-box svg {
  width: 20px; height: 20px;
}
@keyframes arrowUp { 
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.8; } 
  50% { transform: translateY(-3px); opacity: 1; } 
}
@keyframes arrowDown { 
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.8; } 
  50% { transform: translateY(3px); opacity: 1; } 
}

/* 🔸 هندسة قائمة المفضلة ونجمة الكروت (Workspace) 🔸 */
.tc { position: relative; } /* لتموضع النجمة داخل الكارت */

.tc-star-btn {
  position: absolute; top: 6px; left: 6px; width: 24px; height: 24px;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7); border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--b);
  display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
  cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); transition: all 0.2s ease;
  z-index: 10; backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
}

/* إظهار النجمة عند التمرير (للكمبيوتر) أو بشكل خفيف دائم (للموبايل) */
@media (min-width: 769px) { .tc:hover .tc-star-btn { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); } }
@media (max-width: 768px) { .tc-star-btn { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1); } }

.tc-star-btn:hover { border-color: var(--o); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
.tc-star-icon { width: 13px; height: 13px; fill: none; stroke: var(--t3); stroke-width: 2; transition: all 0.2s; }

/* حالة التفعيل (الأداة مفضلة) */
.tc-star-btn.is-fav { opacity: 1 !important; background: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.15) !important; border-color: var(--o) !important; transform: scale(1) !important; }
.tc-star-btn.is-fav .tc-star-icon { stroke: var(--o); fill: var(--o); filter: drop-shadow(0 0 3px rgba(255,106,0,0.6)); }

.star-pop { animation: starPulse 0.3s ease; }
@keyframes starPulse { 0% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.4); } 100% { transform: scale(1); } }

/* تنسيق عناصر القائمة المنسدلة */
.fav-item { 
  display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; 
  padding: 8px 10px; background: var(--s2); border: 1px solid transparent; 
  border-radius: 6px; transition: 0.2s; 
}
.fav-item:hover { border-color: var(--o); background: rgba(255,106,0,0.05); }
.fav-item-link { font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #fff; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; flex: 1; text-align: right; }
.fav-item-link:hover { color: var(--o); }
.fav-item-del { color: var(--t3); padding: 0 5px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1; transition: 0.2s; display: flex; align-items: center; font-weight: bold; }
.fav-item-del:hover { color: #ff4444; transform: scale(1.2); }

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="pg" id="pg-sentiment">
  <div class="tp">
    <div class="th">
      <h1> نبض السوق والمشاعر</h1>
      <p>تحليل شامل يربط بين سيكولوجية المتداولين والمعطيات الفنية</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rc" style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
      <div class="widget-box" style="width: 100%; border-color: var(--o); background: transparent;">
  <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--t2); margin-bottom: 25px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">مؤشر الخوف والطمع الحالي</div>
  
  <div class="fng-classic-wrap" style="transform: scale(1.1); margin: 20px auto 30px auto;">
    <div class="fng-gauge-container">
      <div class="fng-track"></div>
      <div class="fng-needle-wrap" id="sentNeedleWrap">
        <div class="fng-needle" id="sentNeedleBody"></div>
      </div>
