        <span style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace; font-size:0.5rem; color:#1a1a1a; letter-spacing:2px;">360° TRIANGLE PREDICTOR — ADAM THEORY</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
